## 8. Authentication & Security

### 8.1. Authentication Methods
- **SIWE (Sign-In with Ethereum)**: Primary web3 authentication
- **OAuth Integration**: Google, Twitter, Apple social login
- **Email Authentication**: Traditional email/password flow
- **Turnkey Integration**: Secure wallet-based authentication

### 8.2. Session Management
```typescript
// Session provider pattern
export const SessionProvider = ({ children }: { children: ReactNode }) => {
  const updateSession = useCallback(async () => {
    const { user, lastRefreshedAt } = store.getState().auth
    if (shouldRefresh(user, lastRefreshedAt)) {
      await dispatch(refreshUserAction())
    }
  }, [])

  usePoller({ callback: updateSession, interval: 10000 })
  // ... session management logic
}
